text: Inna Moiseeva (Moisseyeva, ; born February 17, 1971) is a Russian rower. ==Biography== She was born on February 17, 1971 in Moscow. She graduated from Moscow State Academy of Physical Culture.Профиль Инны Моисеевой на сайте ИнфоСпорт Member of the Russian team in rowing since 1992. Member of three world championships. In 1998 she became the vice-champion in the race of fours without the helmsman. Prizewinner of the World Cup stages.
